{"type": "article", "id": 16158, "title": "ME Dinner", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-16T06:50:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122439J16O80kaCDzeH4NI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套饭盒，上下两个碗中间放着一个悬空的架子，碗里放着烧烤架，再外面用皮革固定打包，非常适合出门野餐。两个碗隔着烧烤架叠放就是一个简易的加热保温装置。陶瓷制作的锅上面加了一个木质的盖子，让餐具的整体颜色在柔和中分层变化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143518QvuhnV32zpYdILbX.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"799\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143518Py9RTf8w5zc2mUNh.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143519kAtjczuRiVFfSICb.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143520huwVHFL0rqRvYOU8.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}